{"tid":2280231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭訪澳門不需隔離的消息公佈後，隨即成為當地熱話","createTime":"2020-11-10T11:01:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-10T18:26:46.000Z","uid":291865,"like":343,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"3d9816d69e70723b6761e914fcb204382dcbd5a4","tid":2280231,"uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T11:01:12.000Z","msg":"【林鄭大晒? 激嬲澳門人】特首林鄭月娥昨日到訪澳門參加博鰲論壇，同行包括10名政府官員。林鄭訪澳門不需隔離的消息公佈後，隨即成為當地熱話，即便是澳門官媒《澳門日報》或藍絲平台「澳門高登起底組」，各個留言都對事件充斥着不滿情緒，有人認為林鄭來澳是播毒，有人認為任何人都要遵守防疫規則，香港特首都沒有特權；更多澳門人認為，即使在香港有親屬的澳門居民，都無法免隔離來回港澳。<br />\n<br />\n事件更受爭議是，澳門經濟財政司司長早前到訪香港參與何鴻榮之喪禮，回澳後亦遵守防疫規則接受14天隔離，但今次林鄭就擁有特權，澳門市民普遍以此作對比，質疑林鄭並沒有遵守澳門防疫規則，且澳門政府更對她設立特別待遇。<br />\n<br />\n【全文閱讀】<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3kie1WQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3kie1WQ&d=dtUYnMymWvCkGCbOKSm7IhjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=91e79099\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3kie1WQ</a><br />\n－－－－－－－－<br />\n亼 緊貼眾新聞 亼<br />\nFollow TG：<a href=\"https://t.me/hkcnews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkcnews&d=dtUYnMymWvCkGCbOKSm7IhjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=aed7d9ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkcnews</a><br />\nTwitter: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2zykNXc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2zykNXc&d=dtUYnMymWvCkGCbOKSm7IhjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=8d041932\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2zykNXc</a><br />\nIG：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/37AfYcp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F37AfYcp&d=dtUYnMymWvCkGCbOKSm7IhjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=39ff966a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/37AfYcp</a><br />\nYouTube：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/37A1PMI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F37A1PMI&d=dtUYnMymWvCkGCbOKSm7IhjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=05b8735c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/37A1PMI</a>"},{"pid":"875fb6ff6f7c5051d99773b4f76abcb783aeed6f","tid":228023